Text: Please, seed !  I´ve been for hours downloading at a ridiculously low speed, 0 seeders, in spite of saying it has 2 seeders... I don´t see the point of uploading stuff if they are not going to seed it, at least for a few days...
Спасибо за раздачу! А у Вас случайно нет к нему субтитров?
This has actually 3 parts and is more than 7 hours long. Great stuff.

You have to manually copy and paste the screenshot link into the url bar of a new window/tab. Otherwise it won't work, because Imageshack blocks the TPB referrer, i.e. people coming directly from TPB are blocked.
